 Product Manager', 'Comprehensive page performance optimization initiative that reduced loading times by 242% and improved Page Score by 1.45x through cross-team collaboration and systematic monitoring.', 'Page performance directly impacts user experience and business metrics. Cross-functional collaboration is essential for successful performance optimization. Measurement and monitoring are critical for sustained improvements.', null, 24, 'Performance Optimization', true, true, '2025-10-17 11:58:56.948135+00', '2025-10-22 17:09:34.265819+00', 'Growth', 'Technical Optimization', 'Page loading time across platform was not measured initially. When measured, it showed page loading time avg = 8.11 sec and Page Score Avg = 44.3 (web), leading to poor user experience and revenue loss.', 'Established Page loading time dashboard for all customer-facing major pages, conducted analysis, and executed page loading time optimization drive in collaboration with design team, frontend team and content team.', 'In 4 months, page loading time improved by 242% and page score got 1.45x better, helping to reduce dropout from pages and increase revenue.', '[{"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "Established Page loading time dashboard", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "Analyzed performance bottlenecks across platform", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Project Management", "contribution": "Led cross-team optimization drive", "value_chain_position": "midstream"}, {"type": "Stakeholder Management", "contribution": "Collaborated with design, frontend, and content teams", "value_chain_position": "midstream"}]', '[{"label": "Loading Time Improvement", "value": "242%", "category": "Performance", "description": "Page loading time optimization"}, {"label": "Page Score Improvement", "value": "1.45x", "category": "Performance", "description": "Overall page performance score increase"}, {"label": "Timeline", "value": "4 Months", "category": "Timeline", "description": "Project duration and results timeframe"}, {"label": "Initial Performance", "value": "8.11s → Under 3s", "category": "Baseline", "description": "Brought top pages under 3 seconds."}]', ARRAY['performance optimization','loading-time','page-score','data analysis','metrics'], '{"timeline": "4_months", "loading_improvement": "242_percent", "page_score_improvement": "1.45x", "cross_team_collaboration": true}', null, null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', null, null, null, null, null, null), ('8f3e2279-3f0c-4737-9209-ddf4d2547854', 'Assessment Content Automation Workflow', 2026, 'mPower Social Enterprise', 'Product Consultant', 'Developed a high-throughput automation engine for mPower to digitize Cambridge curriculum at scale. Architected an end-to-end extraction-to-DB pipeline with AI-driven quality control.', null, null, 5, 'Automation & AI', true, true, '2026-03-23 10:49:28.751127+00', '2026-03-23 10:49:28.751127+00', 'Scale', 'System Engineering', 'Manual entry of Cambridge past paper questions was slow and error-prone, bottlenecking content scaling.', '- Designed and rapidly developed a multi-stage pipeline: PDF extraction (OCR/Vision) -> CDN asset mapping -> PostgreSQL import.
- Implemented LLM-based automated QC for question verification, explanation generation, and metadata tagging.', '- Scaled the database to 50,000+ AI-verified MCQs and flashcards with 99% automation.
- Transformed content operations from high-latency manual entry to near-instant digital ingestion.', '[{"type": "Pipeline Architecture", "contribution": "Designed end-to-end extraction-to-sync workflow for exam content.", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "AI Integration", "contribution": "Integrated multiple LLMs for pedagogical content generation, formatting, and quality control.", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Rapid Development", "contribution": "Rapidly prototyped and deployed the core automation engine.", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}]', '[{"label": "Workflow Time Reduction", "value": "< 5 Minutes", "category": "Efficiency", "description": "Reduced A/O-level 40-question content generation from 4-5 hours (2 executives) to under 5 minutes with zero human intervention; consolidated a 4-platform process into one agentic workflow."}, {"label": "End-to-End Automation", "value": "Question to Flashcard", "category": "Automation", "description": "Automated questionnaire extraction and image/diagram extraction, and generated right/wrong answer explanations plus practice flashcards."}]', ARRAY['Rapid Development','Automation','AI/ML','Python','System Architecture','Content Engineering','PostgreSQL','Supabase','Azure Blob Storage','PyMuPDF','Pillow','Observability'], '{"database": "PostgreSQL/Supabase", "storage_cdn": "Azure Blob Storage", "data_strategy": "Structured persistence with deduplication at scale", "dataset_scale": "50,000+ records", "observability": "Opik tracing for workflow visibility and cost transparency", "automation_rate": "99%", "ai_generation_qc": "Multiple LLMs for generation, formatting, and quality control", "extraction_stack": ["PyMuPDF (fitz)", "Pillow"], "new_workflow_time": "<5 minutes, zero human intervention", "legacy_workflow_time": "4-5 hours for 40 questions (2 executives)", "orchestration_runtime": "Python", "platform_consolidation": "4 platforms -> 1 agentic workflow"}', null, null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', null, null, null, null, null, null), ('9091cbf7-5089-47dd-b5e9-831aa5da4c5c', 'CareerKi – Workforce EdTech', 2018, 'CareerKi', 'Co-founder & Product Lead', 'CareerKi is a workforce edtech focused on career opportunities in Bangladesh.', 'Building for Bangladesh means designing for accessibility before aesthetics.', null, 6, 'Entrepreneurship', true, true, '2025-10-15 18:53:23.30044+00', '2025-10-21 20:48:44.768144+00', 'Startup', 'Workforce Edtech', 'Bangladesh has the 7th largest labor market in the world, but students & parents had no way to take evidence based decisions to pursue careers.', 'To help students take evidence based career decisions, we researched and profiled 300+ white collar, blue collar and entrepreneurial job roles from labor market with data on salary, technical skills, academic qualification, career challenges, etc. Along with career related evidence based 200 contents, we launched CareerKi in 2018.', 'MAU range: 30K-45K, Till date served over 1.5 million users. ', '[{"type": "Decision Strategy", "contribution": "Ideation, Founding the team, Raised grants from USAID Bangladesh and Govt of Bangladesh", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "UX Design", "contribution": "Product lead, Content development", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}]', '[{"label": "Total Users", "value": "1.5M", "category": "Scale", "description": "Served till 2023"}, {"label": "Monthly Active Users", "value": "30K-45K", "category": "Engagement", "description": "MAU range 2019-2023"}, {"label": "USAID Funding", "value": "$100K+", "category": "Financial", "description": "Grant received"}, {"label": "Job Roles Profiled", "value": "300+", "category": "Content", "description": "Career pathways documented"}, {"label": "Tiger Challenge 2019", "value": "Top 15", "category": "Recognition", "description": "MIT SOLVE Bangladesh startups"}]', ARRAY['entrepreneurship','edtech','research','workforce edtech'], '{"mau": "30K-45K", "users": 1500000, "status": "autopilot", "funding": "$100K+"}', null, null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', null, null, null, null, null, null), ('94668852-c4da-4d92-85ea-9e275e1ef3e4', 'Health Data Copilot', 2026, 'AI Data Automation', 'Product Consultant', 'An automated clinical insight generation system powered by an Orchestrator-led agentic workflow (5 specialized agents), delivering Bangla responses from complex health datasets with end-to-end tracing.', null, null, 16, 'AI & Data Automation', true, true, '2026-03-23 07:56:14.910531+00', '2026-03-23 08:32:42.789398+00', 'Pilot', 'Agentic Workflow', 'Two-fold challenge: (1) Ground-level health workers lacked consumable clinical insights from 300,000+ records for immediate action, and (2) Policy stakeholders lacked ground-truth simulations for evidence-based recommendations.', 'Develop an automated Orchestrator Workflow (Orchestrator, Intent Specialist, SQL Specialist, Data Interpreter, and Policy Analyst) providing rapid Bangla summarization for field workers while enabling complex policy simulation for stakeholders.', 'Successfully deployed a multi-agent system providing sub-second mobile summaries and data-backed policy suggestions with full cost-per-insight transparency.', '[{"type": "AI Architecture", "contribution": "Designed 5-agent Orchestrator Workflow", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Data Engineering", "contribution": "Implemented SQL Schema-on-demand mapping", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Observability", "contribution": "Integrated Opik OTLP cost tracing", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}]', '[{"label": "Pilot Development Time", "value": "2 Weeks", "category": "Delivery", "description": "Developed the pilot with 5 agents-"}, {"label": "Multi-step Execution & Handoffs", "value": "1. Orchestrator", "category": "Agent", "description": "Manages the multi-step execution logic and deterministic agent handoffs."}, {"label": "Bangla & Dialect Parsing", "value": "2. Intent Specialist", "category": "Agent", "description": "Processes broken Bangla and rural dialects into structured JSON intents."}, {"label": "Schema-on-demand Query Generation", "value": "3. SQL Specialist", "category": "Agent", "description": "Generates and executes safe, read-only PostgreSQL queries using a Schema-on-demand approach."}, {"label": "Clinical Risk & Trend Analysis", "value": "4. Data Interpreter", "category": "Agent", "description": "Analyzes clinical values to detect risks (e.g., pre-eclampsia) and identifies health trends for field workers."}, {"label": "WHO/SDG Benchmark Simulation", "value": "5. Policy Analyst", "category": "Agent", "description": "Integrates ground-level data with WHO/SDG international benchmarks to simulate outcomes for policy stakeholders."}]', ARRAY['mastra','agentic-workflow','observability','opik','bangla-summarization','health-data','sql-automation'], '{"agents": [{"name": "Orchestrator", "description": "Manages the multi-step execution logic and deterministic agent handoffs."}, {"name": "Intent Specialist", "description": "Processes broken Bangla and rural dialects into structured JSON intents."}, {"name": "SQL Specialist", "description": "Generates and executes safe, read-only PostgreSQL queries using a Schema-on-demand approach."}, {"name": "Data Interpreter", "description": "Analyzes clinical values to detect risks (e.g., pre-eclampsia) and identifies health trends for field workers."}, {"name": "Policy Analyst", "description": "Integrates ground-level data with WHO/SDG international benchmarks to simulate outcomes for policy stakeholders."}], "framework": "Mastra", "data_records": "300,000+", "workflow_type": "Orchestrator", "agent_hierarchy": "5-Agent"}', null, null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', null, null, null, null, null, null), ('96a41220-6c46-43ca-8450-7b65401f0ae6', 'Free to Paid Conversion Audit', 2023, '10 Minute School', 'Lead Product Manager', 'As PM at 10MS first task- Conducted audits on 50+ dashboards for non-academic product vertical. Found that Free courses & Paid courses CVR significantly different on the platform and none noticed. Hence our project of free to paid users conversion initiated.', 'Dashboard audits reveal hidden insights. Clear metric definitions prevent strategic blind spots.', null, 3, 'Analysis', true, true, '2025-10-15 18:53:23.30044+00', '2025-10-21 21:13:35.789143+00', 'Growth', 'Conversion Optimization', 'At 10MS almost 50+ dashboards and hundreds of metrics were underutilized & underanalyzed to discover business issues or learners issues. When I took over, I wanted to deeply understand these metrics we track and dashboards we maintain.', 'Conducted audits leading to insights and adjustments for enhanced user engagement, LX User journey, Leads management, CVR, and Platform Search.', 'Found that Free courses CVR is 30%+ and Paid course CVR is way low. Hence our strategy for free to paid conversion initiated.', '[{"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "Analysis/dashboard audit", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "Developed product & UX strategies to increase paid conversion", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Decision Strategy", "contribution": "Aligned management and tech team to prioritise paid conversion.", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}]', '[{"label": "Free Course CVR increase", "value": "30% to 45%", "category": "Discovery", "description": "Conversion rate for free courses"}, {"label": "Paid Course CVR", "value": "Maintained between 0.8 to 1.2%", "category": "Discovery", "description": "Fluctuated among courses/products"}, {"label": "Conversion Strategy", "value": "New", "category": "Impact", "description": "Free to paid conversion initiative"}]', ARRAY['analytics','dashboard-audit','conversion','growth','data-analysis','strategy'], '{"free_cvr": "30%+ to 45%", "paid_cvr": "maintained around 0.8-1.2%", "discovery": "CVR gap", "dashboards_audited": 50}', null, null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', null, null, null, null, null, null), ('9809392e-ac82-45d4-9b87-a694c11f837c', 'USAID: Labor Market Assessment', 2021, 'USAID Bangladesh (mPower)', 'Research Analyst', 'Led baseline research on youth labor market and vocational training in Cox''s Bazar for the YES program.', 'Youth livelihood design starts with honest skill vs aspiration mapping.', null, 13, 'Research', true, false, '2025-10-15 18:53:23.30044+00', '2025-10-17 22:24:49.624335+00', 'Research', 'Labor Market Research', 'Lack of youth employment and entrepreneurship insights in post-crisis region.', 'Conduct baseline survey, FGDs, and report writing.', 'Delivered 3 analytical reports that informed USAID program design.', '[{"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "Led field research", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "Authored 3 reports", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Decision Strategy", "contribution": "Labor market analysis.", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}]', '[{"label": "Reports Authored", "value": "3", "category": "Output", "description": "Analytical reports delivered"}, {"label": "Research Region", "value": "Cox''s Bazar", "category": "Scope", "description": "Primary research location"}]', ARRAY['research ops','research design','data analysis','lit review','quant','qual'], '{"region": "Cox Bazar", "reports": 3, "sample_size": "national"}', null, null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', null, null, null, null, null, null), ('9f618897-9168-43ad-bafd-585d1bb68f31', 'Moncho.ai Core Platform & CMS', 2025, 'Moncho', 'Lead Full Stack Engineer', 'Architected the central platform for Moncho.ai, bridging a high-performance public frontend for market exploration with a secure, real-time CMS for internal data governance.', null, null, 25, 'Platform Engineering', true, true, '2026-03-23 12:21:07.385552+00', '2026-03-23 12:31:18.116816+00', 'Scale', 'Full Stack Development', 'Needed a scalable architecture to serve complex, multi-dimensional market intelligence data to users while providing administrators a robust system to manage taxonomy and landscape structures.', '- Engineered the Next.js public application featuring interactive React components for dynamic market maps (e.g., Pricing Scatters, Ecosystem Maps).
- Built a secure internal CMS using Supabase for real-time CRUD operations, role-based access control, and complex relational data modeling.', '- Launched a highly responsive platform enabling users to explore 50+ emerging market sectors visually.
- Streamlined internal data management, allowing the core team to update landscapes and taxonomy instantly without developer intervention.', '[{"type": "Architecture", "contribution": "Designed the end-to-end full stack architecture connecting Next.js with PostgreSQL via Supabase.", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Frontend Engineering", "contribution": "Developed complex, highly interactive data visualization components.", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}]', '[{"label": "Performance", "value": "< 1.5s", "category": "Speed", "description": "Optimized core web vitals resulting in fast load times even on high-density data visualizations."}, {"label": "Data Governance", "value": "Unified CMS", "category": "Operations", "description": "Centralized all data management into a single, secure CMS dashboard."}]', ARRAY['next.js','react','typescript','supabase','postgresql','tailwind css','system design'], '{"auth": "Supabase Auth (Role-based)", "stack": ["Next.js", "Supabase", "TypeScript"], "database": "PostgreSQL with RLS policies", "visualization": "Custom Interactive React Components"}', 'https://www.moncho.ai', null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', 'Moncho.ai', null, null, null, null, null), ('a3dd4a3e-d144-4ee2-bdf1-ead1dbc2e91f', 'Leads Collection Management', 2023, '10 Minute School', 'Lead Product Manager', 'Established new leads collection system that resulted in 262K new leads with 5% CVR & brought visibility of which sources of leads works best to convert a visitor into enrolled learner for the customer support team.', 'Lead source tracking is critical for conversion optimization. What gets measured gets managed.', '/images/projects/lead-management.png', 2, 'Analysis', true, true, '2025-10-15 18:53:23.30044+00', '2025-10-20 15:31:14.199961+00', 'Growth', 'Conversion Optimization', 'Visitors without enrollment or providing any data could watch free videos. And we had no idea, which sources of leads works best for the CX team to convert a visitor into enrolled learner.', 'With the help of Business Intelligence team analyzed data how users see free video on course pages and analyzed if we know which channel/sources of leads works best for CVR.', 'Implemented force log-in to watch free videos in any course page and break down the conversion flow for different channels. Within 6 months collected 262K new leads with 5% CVR & brought visibility of which sources of leads works best to convert a visitor into enrolled learner for the CX team.', '[{"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "Discovery: Identified the flaw in the dashboard", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Decision Strategy", "contribution": "Helped Business Intelligence team to reset the dashboard- defined what is required, why and how we want to visualize it", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}]', '[{"label": "New Leads Collected", "value": "262K", "category": "Growth", "description": "Total new leads generated in 6 months"}, {"label": "Conversion Rate", "value": "Avg 5%", "category": "Conversion", "description": "Lead to enrolled learner CVR"}, {"label": "Channel wise CVR Visibility", "value": "Full", "category": "Analytics", "description": "Complete breakdown by source"}]', ARRAY['growth','conversion','lead-generation','analysis','metrics'], '{"cvr": "5%", "leads_collected": 262000, "channels_tracked": "multiple"}', null, null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', null, null, null, null, null, null), ('a5603511-a9c0-48c5-a14f-8f17e0823890', 'EdTech Market Thesis & $2Mn from Sequoia', 2021, '10 Minute School', 'Strategy Consultant', 'My "Bangladesh Edtech Market Thesis" facilitated a 2Mn investment from Sequoia Capital India in 10MS.', 'Vision must be backed by credible narrative and data — that''s how ecosystems get funded.', null, 5, 'Strategy', true, true, '2025-10-15 18:53:23.30044+00', '2025-10-21 20:54:34.903347+00', 'Research', 'Market Research & Strategic Narrative', 'Edtech funding ecosystem lacked credible data on market size and user adoption.', 'Authored comprehensive market landscape and TAM analysis of Bangladesh''s EdTech sector and different segments. ', 'Enabled Sequoia''s $2M seed investment into 10MS.', '[{"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "Conducted comprehensive market research", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "Authored TAM analysis", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Decision Strategy", "contribution": "Assisted 10MS team to set their long term strategy.", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}]', '[{"label": "Investment Secured", "value": "$2M", "category": "Financial", "description": "Seed funding from Sequoia Capital India"}, {"label": "Total Market Size", "value": "$11.11 Bn", "category": "Market", "description": "Education Market in 2022 (B2B-B2C)"}, {"label": "K-12 After School", "value": "$6.1 Bn", "category": "Market", "description": "Largest market segment"}, {"label": "Upskilling + Hiring", "value": "$1.98 Bn", "category": "Market", "description": "Professional development"}]', ARRAY['strategy','investment','market-research','edtech','fundraising','sequoia'], '{"tam": "$11.11B", "investor": "Sequoia Capital India", "investment_round": "Seed"}', 'https://www.10minuteschool.com', 'https://www.10minuteschool.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/making-sense-edtech-bangladesh-shazzad-hossain-mukit/', null, '[]', '[]', '[{"url": "https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/making-sense-edtech-bangladesh-shazzad-hossain-mukit/", "label": "LinkedIn Article"}, {"url": "https://drive.google.com/file/d/example-report.pdf", "label": "Full Report PDF"}]', '[]', null, null, 'EdTech Analysis Article', null, null, null), ('aa5f8b0c-a5bb-4a7e-a634-c915f75c521d', 'World Bank IFC Survey on 10MS Impact', 2022, '10 Minute School', 'Research Lead', 'Led World Bank IFC Survey on 4.7K students to measure the impact of 10MS on delivering quality education.', 'Research collaboration with international institutions validates product impact and builds credibility.', null, 1, 'Analysis', true, true, '2025-10-15 18:53:23.30044+00', '2025-10-22 14:08:56.062869+00', 'Research', 'Impact Assessment', 'World Bank IFC wanted to understand the impact of 10MS on K-12 students across Bangladesh in different locations both for paid and free courses.', 'I was the research lead for the project.', 'At 10MS we did not have concrete data about our impact on access to quality education across Bangladesh. Data shows 10MS is more popular in rural and suburban areas than metropolitan cities as students at these places lack access to quality teachers and educational contents.', '[{"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "Research design & planning", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "Data cleaning & result analysis using tableau", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Decision Strategy", "contribution": "Report preparation", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}]', '[{"label": "Students Surveyed", "value": "4,781", "category": "Research", "description": "+46 Parents"}, {"label": "Rural & Semi-Urban Users", "value": "66%", "category": "Demographics", "description": "From villages and district cities"}, {"label": "High Performers", "value": "50%", "category": "Academic Impact", "description": "Scored 80-100 in last academic year"}, {"label": "Positive Impact", "value": "78%", "category": "Satisfaction", "description": "Agreed 10MS has positive impact (45% Strongly, 33% Agree)"}, {"label": "~50+ (Free)", "value": "39 (Avg)", "category": "Satisfaction", "description": "Net Promoter Score"}]', ARRAY['research','impact-assessment','research ops','tableau','data-analysis'], '{"nps": 39, "rural_users": "66%", "survey_size": 4781, "gender_split": "32.5% female, 66% male"}', null, null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', null, null, null, null, null, null), ('b33013ab-ce46-4757-8653-049c3a892412', 'HSEP Florida State University', 2024, '10 Minute School x USAID x FSU', 'Lead Product Manager', 'Co-led USAID-funded HSEP initiative to roll out comprehensive LMS for 3,000 colleges and train 60,000 teachers. Discontinued, due to dismantling of USAID.', 'National-scale learning projects require institutional buy-in and teacher-first UX.', null, 10, 'Digital Public Infrastructure', true, true, '2025-10-15 18:53:23.30044+00', '2025-10-21 21:16:31.126275+00', 'Feature Suit', 'B2B', 'Bangladesh lacked digital teaching infrastructure at high school level for 140K+ teachers and would take 50+ years for Govt to physically train all teachers. ', 'Design comprehensive LMS for learning rollout, coordinate with FSU, Chemonics Int, A2i & Education Ministry/DSHE.', 'Secured $3M grant; trained 500 teachers and led the prototyping of the platform in 21 days. Later discontinued (USAID).', '[{"type": "Decision Strategy", "contribution": "Planned and applied to the public tender. Secured USAID grant", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "UX Design", "contribution": "Designed comprehensive LMS end to end user journey for several feature suits- PLC, P2P asssessment, Discussion, etc.", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Decision Strategy", "contribution": "Led teacher training of the system countrywide.", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}]', '[{"label": "Master Trainee Teachers Trained", "value": "500", "category": "Impact", "description": "Nationwide teacher training program"}, {"label": "Prototype", "value": "21 days", "category": "DPI", "description": "Digital Infrastructure Plan Design"}, {"label": "Budget Secured", "value": "$3M", "category": "Financial", "description": "USAID grant funding. Later Discontinued."}]', ARRAY['complex stakeholder management','lms','project management','Govt project','national scale','DPI'], '{"reach": "nationwide", "budget": "$3M", "target_teachers": 60000, "target-institutions": 3000}', null, null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', null, null, null, null, null, null), ('b495ab11-29f3-43be-a253-ac9ade03f66d', 'Co-authored book on SMEs digital adoption', 2022, 'Friedrich-Ebert-Stiftung (FES) x SME Foundation
