 Alam Khan, Shazzad Hossain Mukit. International Journal of SME Development, Issue 05, Jun 2022"}]', '[]', null, null, null, null, null, null), ('be82af94-bbe2-42e7-8d00-3fca701dad03', 'Certificate Sharing Journey Optimization', 2023, '10 Minute School', 'Lead Product Manager', 'Optimized certificate sharing functionality to increase organic traffic and user engagement through improved public pages, profile sections, and tracking capabilities.', 'Certificate sharing is crucial for organic growth and peer-to-peer marketing. Technical improvements combined with user experience enhancements can significantly impact engagement metrics.', null, 22, 'Product Optimization', true, true, '2025-10-17 11:58:56.948135+00', '2025-10-17 22:14:37.457385+00', 'Feature Suit', 'Growth', 'Certificate was the key way to signal positive learning outcome among peers and becoming a major way to increase organic traffic. However, the sharing experience had technical issues and lacked proper tracking.', 'Certificate Public Page UI Fix and PDP Redirection, Certificate (Profile) section sharing issue fix, UTM parameter added to Certificate public URLs for data tracking, Paid certificate template change.', 'Within 6 months, increased Avg Certificates downloads by 66.11% and increased Avg visitors by 91.62%.', '[{"type": "UX Design", "contribution": "Certificate Public Page UI Fix and PDP Redirection", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}, {"type": "Technical Implementation", "contribution": "Certificate (Profile) section sharing issue fix", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}, {"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "UTM parameter added to Certificate public URLs for data tracking", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Product Strategy", "contribution": "Paid certificate template change", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}]', '[{"label": "Certificate Downloads Increase", "value": "66.11%", "category": "Growth", "description": "Average certificates downloads improvement"}, {"label": "Visitor Increase", "value": "91.62%", "category": "Growth", "description": "Average visitors improvement"}, {"label": "Timeline", "value": "6 Months", "category": "Timeline", "description": "Project duration and results timeframe"}]', ARRAY['certification','analysis','organic-growth','tracking','optimization','product-enhancement'], '{"timeline": "6_months", "utm_tracking": "implemented", "visitors_increase": "91.62_percent", "downloads_increase": "66.11_percent"}', null, null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', null, null, null, null, null, null), ('d20b1578-b515-4e29-88e7-0ec866504399', 'Group Guidance/Roadmaps', 2025, '10 Minute School', 'Consultant
