', true, true, '2025-10-15 18:53:23.30044+00', '2026-03-23 08:27:26.54305+00', 'Feature Suit', 'Rapid Prototyping', 'STEM graduates required guided mentorship to bridge their skills gaps to lands jobs. ', 'Architected a 3-role ecosystem. Implemented TaRL logic for threshold-driven content unlocking and Spaced Repetition (SM-2 based) for assessment retention. Designed Supabase RLS policies for role-based access.', 'Product RnD deployed in record time of 4 days to seek users feedback. ', '[{"type": "System Architecture", "contribution": "Scaled to a 3-role ecosystem (Student, Mentor, Admin). Designed RBAC and batch orchestration logic.", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Adaptive Pedagogy", "contribution": "Implemented TaRL (competency-based unlocking) and Spaced Repetition algorithms for personalized learning.", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Vibe coding", "contribution": "Rapidly prototyped and iterated features in record time using Cursor and AI-driven development.", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}]', '[{"label": "Define to Deployment", "value": "04 Days", "category": "Rapid Prototyping", "description": "Initial MVP developed in record time."}, {"label": "Adaptive Unlocking", "value": "TaRL Logic", "category": "Pedagogy", "description": "80% competency required to unlock new content."}, {"label": "Retention Logic", "value": "Spaced Repetition", "category": "Assessment", "description": "Optimized memory retention via flashcard practice."}]', ARRAY['Vibe Coding','TaRL','Spaced Repetition','Adaptive Learning','RBAC','Batch Orchestration','Rapid Prototyping'], '{"User Roles": 3, "rapid_prototyping": "04 Days", "Human Resources Required": 1}', null, null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', null, null, null, null, '/images/projects/group-guidance-demo-poster.jpg', '/images/projects/group-guidance-demo.webm'), ('d31b5b0b-7055-45d6-ba2a-e857cc7fe859', 'Quizards – Bangla Edutainment Platform', 2014, 'Quizards', 'Co-founder & Product Lead', 'Quizards a Bangla edutainment web platform.', 'Learned to ship fast and iterate with early community feedback.', '/images/projects/quizards.png', 7, 'Entrepreneurship', true, true, '2025-10-15 18:53:23.30044+00', '2025-10-21 20:42:30.731896+00', 'Startup', 'Edutainment Edtech', 'Wanted to create a national platform in Bangla language to practice general knowledge trivia in interactive form.', 'To promote inquisitiveness among youngs in Bangla language, I co-founded Quizards in 2014.', 'Served over 0.25 million users. MAU range: 1.2K-1.5K. Currently we do not work for quizards, it is in autopilot mode.', '[{"type": "Decision Strategy", "contribution": "Co-founded Quizards platform", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "UX Design", "contribution": "Designed gamified quiz mechanics", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}]', '[{"label": "Total Users", "value": "250K", "category": "Scale", "description": "Served till date"}, {"label": "Monthly Active Users", "value": "1.2K-1.5K", "category": "Engagement", "description": "MAU range"}, {"label": "Online Start-ups Bangladesh 2016", "value": "Top 10", "category": "Recognition", "description": "Award by G&R"}, {"label": "BRAC Manthan Digital Innovation Award 2016", "value": "Special Mention", "category": "Recognition", "description": "Journalism and entertainment"}]', ARRAY['entrepreneurship','edutainment','gamification','quiz'], '{"mau": "1.2K-1.5K", "users": 250000, "status": "autopilot", "language": "Bangla"}', null, null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', null, null, null, null, null, null), ('d7aaaaa5-6892-4586-9d18-2731a9009b3d', 'Course Validity Date Implementation', 2023, '10 Minute School', 'Lead Product Manager', 'Implemented course validity dates to drive user progress and course completion by creating urgency and clear deadlines for learners.', 'Adding time constraints to courses can significantly improve user engagement and completion rates. Clear deadlines create psychological urgency that drives action.', null, 23, 'Product Strategy', true, true, '2025-10-17 11:58:56.948135+00', '2025-10-17 22:17:17.782118+00', 'Feature', 'Learning Experience
', 'After purchasing courses, users were not progressing or finishing courses, leading to poor completion rates and reduced learning outcomes.', 'Implemented Course validation date system to create urgency and drive user engagement with clear deadlines for course completion.', 'In 6 months, increased user course progress (for first 7 days) from 48% to 77%.', '[{"type": "Product Strategy", "contribution": "Designed course validity date system", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Technical Implementation", "contribution": "Implemented course validation date functionality", "value_chain_position": "midstream"}, {"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "Monitored and optimized user progress metrics", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}]', '[{"label": "Progress Improvement", "value": "48% → 77%", "category": "Engagement", "description": "User course progress increase in first 7 days"}, {"label": "Timeline", "value": "6 Months", "category": "Timeline", "description": "Project duration and results timeframe"}, {"label": "Feature Implementation", "value": "Validity Date", "category": "Technical", "description": "Course expiration system for urgency"}]', ARRAY['UX','learning experience','engagement','completion-rates','product-strategy'], '{"timeline": "6_months", "validity_system": "implemented", "progress_improvement": "48_to_77_percent"}', null, null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', null, null, null, null, null, null), ('e1f70ba7-585b-4895-b5c4-5ca35136fb77', 'Course Rating System', 2023, '10 Minute School', 'Lead Product Manager', 'Introduced a new trust-based course rating metric — % of users rating 5/5.', 'Trust-based metrics often provide more meaningful signals than traditional average ratings for educational content.', '/images/projects/rating-system.png', 21, 'Trust & Credibility', true, true, '2025-10-17 09:56:44.34014+00', '2025-10-21 21:08:03.6564+00', 'Feature', 'Rating System Innovation', 'Traditional rating systems didn''t effectively communicate course quality and credibility to learners. Most of them mention, number of users rating 4 and above. ', 'Conceptualized and implemented rating logic for credibility benchmarking using percentage of 5-star ratings. 
', 'First-of-its-kind course rating approach so far we knew.', '[{"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "Analyzed platform wide ratings for all the major courses.", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Data Analysis", "contribution": "Conceptualized trust-based rating metric (% of 5-star ratings)", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "UX Design", "contribution": "Implemented rating logic for credibility benchmarking", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}]', '[{"label": "Innovation", "value": "First-of-its-kind", "category": "Innovation", "description": "New rating approach in Edtech"}, {"label": "Rating Metric", "value": "5/5 Percentage", "category": "Features", "description": "Trust-based credibility measure"}]', ARRAY['rating-system','analysis','credibility','innovation','UI/UX','rapid prototyping'], '{"scope": "bangladesh_global", "metric": "5_star_percentage", "innovation": "first_of_kind"}', null, null, null, null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', null, null, null, null, null, null), ('e40c2d0c-5918-4f01-8c25-54457d1c3d35', 'Agentic Search & Intelligence Pipelines', 2026, 'Moncho', 'AI/Backend Engineer', 'Engineered high-throughput "Agentic RAG" workflows using Mastra to automate sector mapping, price discovery, and organizational data enrichment without relying on static vector databases.', null, null, 27, 'Automation & AI', true, true, '2026-03-23 12:21:07.385552+00', '2026-03-23 12:31:18.116816+00', 'Scale', 'AI Engineering', 'Manual market research across international regions, pricing synthesis, and top-down market sizing calculations was too slow to map 50+ emerging market sectors.', '- Replaced static vector RAG with a dynamic "Agentic RAG" pipeline, using Tavily and Exa APIs to retrieve real-time, primary-source market data while actively filtering out aggregator domains.
- Integrated the Vercel AI SDK to feed search context into LLMs, enforcing strict Zod schemas to guarantee structured JSON outputs for market sizes and currency-adjusted prices.', '- Fully automated complex sector calculations and competitive price gathering, reducing strategic research time from hours to under 60 seconds.
- Successfully mapped 50+ sectors autonomously, establishing a near-instant digital ingestion pipeline with high-confidence source citations.', '[{"type": "AI Integration", "contribution": "Built tool-based Agentic RAG workflows bypassing the need for static vector stores.", "value_chain_position": "upstream"}, {"type": "Pipeline Orchestration", "contribution": "Designed high-throughput data extraction using strictly enforced Zod schemas.", "value_chain_position": "downstream"}]', '[{"label": "Workflow Automation", "value": "90% Reduction", "category": "Efficiency", "description": "Dropped strategic manual research time per org/sector from hours to under a minute."}, {"label": "Pipeline Throughput", "value": "50+ Sectors", "category": "Scale", "description": "Processed thousands of market data points autonomously via dynamic web-based RAG."}]', ARRAY['mastra','agentic rag','vercel ai sdk','zod','tavily','exa api','typescript'], '{"llm_usage": "Multi-LLM orchestration", "throughput": "50+ sectors mapped autonomously", "architecture": "Tool-based Web RAG (No Vector DB)", "agent_framework": "Mastra", "data_validation": "Strict Zod Schemas", "core_capabilities": ["Price Benchmarking", "Market Sizing", "Org Enrichment"], "retrieval_engines": ["Tavily API", "Exa API"]}', 'https://www.moncho.ai', null, 'https://www.moncho.ai/blog/monchos-agentic-workflow-part-1', null, '[]', '[]', '[]', '[]', 'Moncho.ai', null, 'Moncho Agentic Workflow Blog', null, null, null), ('f6adecd5-1c59-4a03-9927-09867573c57b', 'DAEF: Digital Economy & Sectoral Analysis', 2021, 'Innovision Consulting', 'Portfolio Manager', 'Assisted to set up DAEF team to study digital economy, consumer behavior, and startup ecosystems across Bangladesh.
