n-non-academic-research', 'invitation', 'Making Sense of Non-Academic Research 101', 'Workshop on translating non-academic research into actionable product insights.', 'View workshop deck', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tMkvqUVUZIeAX2n7WSWcjY5llNdZxZZ5/view?usp=sharing', 3, '2025-11-08 18:16:51.303358+00', '2025-11-08 18:16:51.303358+00');;
